they exist in the world that surrounds them, shaped by the systems they exist in, shaped by those who exist in the systems that they themselves
exist in...

"No one likes to be criticized, but everyone
loves to be understood."(p.58, processing manual) - this stands out to me as being so central to so much in the work that I do and
the things I engage with that matter to me.

